TI  - Building a framework towards climate-smart agriculture in the Yangambi landscape, Democratic Republic of Congo (DRC)
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
