TI  - Assessing climate-smart agroforestry practices: a study of tree species composition, distribution, and utilities in two contrasting agroecosystems of Rwanda
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Smart farming
KW  - Climate resilience
