TI  - Harnessing indigenous knowledge and practices for effective adaptation in the Sahel
T2  - CURRENT OPINION IN ENVIRONMENTAL SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - WEST-AFRICA
KW  - AGRICULTURE
KW  - VARIABILITY
