TI  - Effects of socio-ecological factors on the pastoralists-farmers conflicts in Nigeria's Mid-Benue Trough
T2  - REMOTE SENSING APPLICATIONS-SOCIETY AND ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Conflict
KW  - Farmer
KW  - Mid-Benue Trough
KW  - Pastoralist
