TI  - Climate-Smart Agriculture (CSA) practices and food security among smallholder farmers in Ghana: a case study of Sekyere Kumawu District
T2  - REGIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Climate-smart agriculture
