TI  - Understanding rice production stagnation in the Philippines: Regional evidence and development implications
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - FOOD SECURITY
KW  - ADAPTIVE CAPACITY
KW  - SOUTHEAST-ASIA
