TI  - Effect of climate variability on crop income and indigenous adaptation strategies of households
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Household
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Determinants
KW  - Climate variability
