TI  - Effect of farmer-herder conflict adaptation strategies on multidimensional poverty and subjective wellbeing in Ghana
T2  - AFRICAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL AND RESOURCE ECONOMICS-AFJARE
LA  - English
KW  - farmer-herder conflict
KW  - adaptation strategies
KW  - multidimensional poverty
