TI  - A Ricardian valuation of the impact of climate change on Nigerian cocoa production: Insight for adaptation policy
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Nigeria
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate change projections
KW  - Net revenue per farm hectare
