TI  - Assessing gender-specific training needs for climate-smart agriculture in the upland Shan region of Myanmar: a comparison between climate-smart and non-climate-smart villages
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
