TI  - Reaching out? Governing weather and climate services (WCS) for farmers
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Weather and climate services
KW  - Governance
KW  - Agro-meteorological services
KW  - Climate adaptation
