TI  - Farmers' Awareness in the Context of Climate Change: An Underutilized Way for Ensuring Sustainable Farmland Adaptation and Surface Water Quality
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - crop water requirements
KW  - irrigated agriculture
KW  - paddy fields
KW  - soil water balance
KW  - Surface Storage Capacity
