TI  - Impact of sustainable intensification technologies on farm income among rural households: Empirical evidence from Dedza district, Malawi
T2  - AFRICAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL AND RESOURCE ECONOMICS-AFJARE
LA  - English
