TI  - A bitter pill: smallholder responses to the new green revolution prescriptions in northern Ghana
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT AND WORLD ECOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - development
