TI  - Mining Extractivism, Climate Stress, and Water Injustice: A Case Study of the Proposed Jindal Iron-Ore Mine in Melmoth, KwaZulu-Natal and Hydrosocial Justice
T2  - SOCIAL SCIENCES-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - mining
