TI  - Spatial ecological risk assessment of Kaeng Krachan national park, Thailand (UNESCO world heritage site) through integration of AHP, Shannon's entropy, and Monte Carlo simulation
T2  - MODELING EARTH SYSTEMS AND ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
