TI  - Integrated crop water management might sustainably halve the global food gap
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH LETTERS
LA  - English
KW  - sustainable intensification
KW  - yield gap
KW  - water harvesting
KW  - conservation agriculture
KW  - irrigation efficiency
