TI  - Unlocking food security and livelihoods: the transformative power of agroecology among vulnerable smallholder farmers in Kembata Tembaro, Ethiopia
T2  - AGROECOLOGY AND SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Ethiopia
