TI  - Impact of Adoption of Climate-smart Practices on Horticulture Yield: Lessons from Smallholder Horticulture Empowerment and Promotion Approach in Ethiopia
T2  - JOURNAL OF THE FACULTY OF AGRICULTURE KYUSHU UNIVERSITY
