TI  - Enhancing farmers' access and use of conserved germplasm for improved food security and climate resilience: The case of sorghum at Kenya's national genebank
T2  - PLANT GENETIC RESOURCES-CHARACTERIZATION AND UTILIZATION
LA  - English
KW  - farmer-preferred traits
KW  - genebank
KW  - germplasm evaluation
KW  - germplasm user group
