TI  - Which is more important to sorghum production systems in the Sudano-Sahelian zone of West Africa: Climate change or improved management practices?
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Crop modeling
KW  - Soil fertility
KW  - Temperature
KW  - Heterogeneity
KW  - Agriculture
KW  - Management
KW  - Climate change
KW  - CHANGE ADAPTATION
