TI  - Adaptive behavior of farmers under consecutive droughts results in more vulnerable farmers: a large-scale agent-based modeling analysis in the Bhima basin, India
T2  - NATURAL HAZARDS AND EARTH SYSTEM SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
