TI  - Does disaster shocks affect farmers' willingness for insurance? Mediating effect of risk perception and survey data from risk-prone areas in East China
T2  - NATURAL HAZARDS
LA  - English
KW  - Natural hazards
KW  - Risk perception
KW  - Resilience
KW  - Weather aberrations
