TI  - Policy and Legal Frameworks Governing Trees: Incentives or Disincentives for Smallholder Tree Planting Decisions in Cameroon?
T2  - SMALL-SCALE FORESTRY
LA  - English
KW  - Agroforestry
KW  - Poverty reduction
KW  - Millennium development goals
KW  - Ecosystem services
KW  - Policies and legislation
