TI  - Variations in the potential climatic suitability distribution patterns and grain yields for spring maize in Northeast China under climate change
T2  - CLIMATIC CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - 3 PROVINCES
KW  - CROPPING SYSTEM
KW  - VARIABILITY
KW  - CLASSIFICATION
KW  - RESOURCES
